item.title: Soccerio
item.description: While playing Head Football Champions League 2014 15 you have a unique opportunity to show yourself as a real professional who can play not only with his feet, but also with his head. You get into the Champions League, where you will try to win the Challenge Cup. Choose your favorite player and start the competition. Everything is very simple - hit the ball with your head from your own half of the field, and also try to score more goals into the opponent’s goal.

item.title: The Smurfs Football Match
item.description: Football competitions have always attracted many people of different generations. If you want to play unusual football with heads or arrange a small competition, this game is just for you. Choose your team, define the conditions, and start your way to victory. Train and win cup after cup.
